channel.title: Some Aussie jokes and stuff
channel.description:
So I was on IRC, and all of the brits were being anti-Australian. Anyway, thuglife linked me to this site: www.ozjokes.com Took a look, and I thought people would get a good laugh out of these. :P I picked a few that resemble my own lifestyle.
An introduction: http://www.ozjokes.com/content/view/521/30/
One of our hierarchical systems: http://www.ozjokes.com/content/view/1055/30/
Various differences between Australia and other nations: http://www.ozjokes.com/content/view/638/30/
Australian SAS related: http://www.ozjokes.com/content/view/654/30/
